OL,3,CLocal elections 2026: Results from the
OL,4,CSouth, South-east and Thames Valley
OL,6,FThis year's local elections are
OL,7,Fdescribed as "crucial" for the
OL,8,FMeridian region, with the stakes high
OL,9,Ffor all the main political parties.
OL,11,FAll seats are to play for on county
OL,12,Fcouncils in Essex, Hampshire, and East
OL,13,Fand West Sussex.
OL,15,FIn addition, Surrey has its first set
OL,16,Fof elections to new East and West
OL,17,Funitary authorities, following the
OL,18,Fabolition of their county and district
OL,19,Fcouncils.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
