OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778351315
OL,3,CLocal elections 2026: Results from the
OL,4,CSouth, South-east and Thames Valley
OL,6,FBig battles will also be fought in
OL,7,Funitary authorities with all seats in
OL,8,Fplay in Southampton, Portsmouth and on
OL,9,Fthe Isle of Wight.
OL,11,FAttention will also be focussed on
OL,12,Fboroughs and districts where half or a
OL,13,Fthird of council seats are up.
OL,15,FIn Southend-on-Sea which was one of
OL,16,Fthe first areas to reveal results, the
OL,17,Fcouncil remains in no overall control.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
