OL,3,CLocal elections 2026: Results from the
OL,4,CSouth, South-east and Thames Valley
OL,6,FIn Reading, Labour has held control of
OL,7,Fthe borough council, but there were
OL,8,Fcelebrations for the Green Party who
OL,9,Fsecured several seats.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian, Councillor
OL,12,FDave McElroy who represents the Green
OL,13,FParty in Reading Central said: "To
OL,14,Fhave had such a hard week with the
OL,15,Frelentless coverage, and for the
OL,16,Fpublic to go 'enough is enough - we're
OL,17,Fready for change' is just mind-blowing.
OL,19,F"I'm speechless."
OL,21,FCounting is also underway in Oxford.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
